textBeforeTable: Color: Blue Size: 10" x 30" Tuff End fenders are for heavy duty marine applications. Constructed from the same flexible, resilient vinyl as our Super Gard, Big B, and Hull Gard fenders, the end in each Tuff End fender is injection molded for extra strength and reliability. Tuff End fenders are designed to perform under the most demanding conditions. Tuff End Inflatable Vinyl Fenders feature seamless construction, the strongest in the industry! Reviews Description
textAfterTable: Recommended inflation is 2 psi. * The most accurate way to select the right fender for your boat is to survey your docking area to find out what fender is in use for the same size and weight of boat, in terms of fender dimensions and quantities, and use that as a guideline.   Product Details Manufacturer: Taylor Made Products Product SKU: TM-41188
